{"tid":1971852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"塞爾維亞到處現「感謝您，習大哥」巨型廣告","createTime":"2020-04-14T07:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T04:49:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9d8f5ee52c71820932d7da3e31340e934c94871c","tid":1971852,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T07:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2615000/2617100/3243_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2615000%2F2617100%2F3243_1024.jpg&h=95fdfdd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n位於東歐巴爾幹半島的塞爾維亞（Serbia），首都貝爾格萊德（Belgrade）街上近日出現大型電子屏幕廣告牌。屏幕上以中國國旗為背景，在中國國家主席習近平旁邊，打出「感謝您，習大哥」字樣。<br />\n<br />\n上月中全國進入緊急狀態的塞爾維亞，在總統武契奇（Aleksandar Vucic）向中國求救後隨即得到回應，上月 21 日中國派出 6 人專家醫療隊，連同呼吸機、口罩、試劑盒等十數噸抗疫物資，飛赴首都貝爾格萊德。<br />\n<br />\n武契奇當時在機場以紅地氈親迎，更當場親吻中國國旗。中國專家在塞國幫助抗疫工作，武契奇亦多次透過媒體感謝中國相助，在當地不少地方都可見到「感謝您，習大哥」的廣告牌。<br />\n<br />\n塞爾維亞官員也對路透社表示，受中國專家的指導，現在塞國開始進行全面性普篩，以找出更多新冠肺炎患者。<br />\n<br />\n除了塞爾維亞，北京又派出醫療隊伍到柬埔寨、伊朗、伊拉克、寮國、巴基斯坦、委內瑞拉，以及唯一參與「一帶一路」的七國集團國、疫情嚴峻的意大利，上周中國又派出 12 人專家小組到菲律賓，幫助當地政府抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n不過，歐美國家卻不滿中國隱瞞疫情。在昨日的白宮記者會上，有記者問美國總統特朗普：「為甚麼中國隱瞞疫情，到現在還沒有承擔因果報應（consequence）？」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普隨即回答，「你怎麼知道沒有報應？我當然不會告訴你，中國會知道的，我為甚麼要告訴你」，可見特朗普的憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://china.hket.com/article/2617100/%E3%80%90%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E6%82%A8%EF%BC%8C%E7%BF%92%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5%E3%80%8D%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%20%E6%96%BC%E5%A1%9E%E7%88%BE%E7%B6%AD%E4%BA%9E%E9%9A%A8%E8%99%95%E5%8F%AF%E8%A6%8B?mtc=20023</code></pre>"},{"pid":"1047cd86a2dc807656e25c1b0b7bec3bbd8279a7","tid":1971852,"uid":74622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T07:43:11.000Z","msg":"聽講美國通緝緊 但中國去幫佢 搞到侵侵好嬲<br />\n希望唔好似啲連登仔打好嬲呀就算啦"},{"pid":"a047bc16101b4f5fb35660d6595e66a989b0e3a7","tid":1971852,"uid":54386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T07:43:42.000Z","msg":"你怎麼知道沒有報應？我當然不會告訴你，中國會知道的，我為甚麼要告訴你<br />\n希望侵侵唔係得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f209fd6a288297d9970fcce4116b5d1f07416a","tid":1971852,"uid":156936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:37:05.000Z","msg":"等回力標"},{"pid":"cefbce6f7ef2c2b0bbf8b8c50c02960230d68114","tid":1971852,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:39:51.000Z","msg":"比美軍炸完所以特別親中？"},{"pid":"cbfe78a49c5bf600c98b9afb839629c88d1469c7","tid":1971852,"uid":185656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cefbce6f7ef2c2b0bbf8b8c50c02960230d68114","tid":1971852,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:39:51.000Z","msg":"比美軍炸完所以特別親中？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:42:23.000Z","msg":"你睇返南斯拉夫歷史,就會知Serbia本身都係賤種國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7573af67536945c6ac9ff01150ea2cb0302771","tid":1971852,"uid":122867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個景都cheap 閪晒"},{"pid":"9900716d2f9b094e5537173f7077db095772cbe9","tid":1971852,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:51:20.000Z","msg":"多數好快中回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296a99f1ccae025316e15fd18ee391d9ef336c33","tid":1971852,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cbfe78a49c5bf600c98b9afb839629c88d1469c7","tid":1971852,"uid":185656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cefbce6f7ef2c2b0bbf8b8c50c02960230d68114